highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Pune. Kesariya is the highest at #1.
Rasiya by Pritam, Shreya Ghoshal, and TUSHAR JOSHI is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Pune, up 65 spots at #13.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Pune the longest, at 51 weeks straight.
